  "special": {
    "title": "The gun of the Bulls.",
    "description": "Always non-elemental. Each shot has a high chance to fire an extra projectile, and aiming triggers a very large Dahl burst. The projectiles follow a distinctive bull-shaped pattern, with greatly reduced recoil in exchange for slightly lower accuracy."
  },
  "notes": "It has a fixed spawn in Frostburn Canyon, making it easy to farm. It does not scale in Normal Mode, or in TVHM until the story is finished. It is especially strong on Gaige, since Close Enough and Anarchy reduce the need for accuracy and the fast empty-reload rhythm suits her well. Stocks matter relatively little aside from a Dahl stock adding one extra burst shot; grip and accessory choice matter far more. It can stay useful well into UVHM, but level scaling still matters.",
